T.png&h=46ac0ca6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/5d82WQL96JI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F5d82WQL96JI&d=X54jjuw0UQFZuhWzkrVO7kzlOXIvf7DEkQzrkg%2FJo1w%3D&h=dd364778\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/5d82WQL96JI</a>"},{"pid":"c0057c110655fa30f4235fd1647bdff7f731e341","tid":2183601,"uid":25952,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-01T05:28:05.000Z","msg":"咁多證據 已經足夠證明係他殺啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n班警咁急燒屍又話無可疑<br />\n最大可能會係邊個殺<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"706f5102ae056ba15bc3b274ef2962fc8e558b0b","tid":2183601,"uid":237487,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-01T05:29:30.000Z","msg":"Wiki<br />\n溺斃的屍體通常會根據體形不同而有的一直浮在水面，有的沉入海底。沉入海底的屍體經過一段時間後會隨着體內腐爛加劇産生氣體而膨脹上浮，這種屍體的膨脹現象被警察形容為「形似巨人」，其死狀通常與生前容貌差異極大，甚至連親屬都無從辨認。流入耳道的水會隨之增加，繼而進入內耳的半規管而影響人的平衡感知，使泳手失去平衡，從而溺斃。[來源請求]"},{"pid":"7b32366d82d92b773ddd00969e79bb1f7822db76","tid":2183601,"uid":114097,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-01T05:29:42.000Z","msg":"咩法醫嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c29ef92033e09c80e88a0edd59f21dd4e0e31dd9","tid":2183601,"uid":296369,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-01T05:30:45.000Z","msg":"呢個法醫唔肯定嘅嘢好可能有，咁快燒咗屍體係咪想毁滅證據？<br />\n通常專業人士都係講嘢模棱兩可，一來可以推卸責任，二來自己又唔使孭鑊.....如果佢係受政權指示或有勢力人士咁樣做咁樣講，佢真係要等天收，死咗都唔會放過佢⋯⋯"},{"pid":"8f2abb02731918dcc2e2d4a1f22bce8e08ccc43b","tid":2183601,"uid":301152,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"c0057c110655fa30f4235fd1647bdff7f731e341","tid":2183601,"uid":25952,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-01T05:28:05.000Z","msg":"咁多證據 已經足夠證明係他殺啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n班警咁急燒屍又話無可疑<br />\n最大可能會係邊個殺<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"