601,"uid":190579,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"144b1e0971a3fece4ccf55285e910ab41727d9cb","tid":2183601,"uid":299514,"like":16,"dislike":10,"score":6,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-09-01T04:46:27.000Z","msg":"咁依個法醫都好撚廢"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-01T05:42:12.000Z","msg":"如果真係自殺點會驗唔到<br />\n佢話唔知 啫係唔係自殺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a4bf101f0b1f18e5525d6813f2bb0b6fdb5e8b7c","tid":2183601,"uid":301152,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"03c91733b0fadaffd2e43aca6e6696316e4d42b5","tid":2183601,"uid":301152,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-01T05:22:31.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1547190-20200901.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1547190-20200901.htm&d=X54jjuw0UQFZuhWzkrVO7kzlOXIvf7DEkQzrkg%2FJo1w%3D&h=34a697eb\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1547190-20200901.htm&h=f02eb778\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1547190-20200901.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n李毓樺說，死者的生殖器官沒有傷痕，子宮和盤骨正常，但很多時受性侵犯未必會在私處留下傷痕，因此不能證實死者生前有否被性侵犯。他又說，<span class=\"red\">有檢取死者的陰道拭子樣本交予警方，轉交化驗所化驗有否精液成份，</span>但他手上沒有這份報告資料。<br />\n<br />\n李毓樺說，遇溺可能是其中一個死亡原因，但不能完全確定，又說一個<span class=\"red\">懂得游水的人選擇跳海自殺並不常見</span>。在<span class=\"red\">死者右胸腔找到50毫升深紅色腐爛液體，左邊找到550亳升</span>。醫管局大律師引述另一名專家證人馬宣立的報告指出，一般遇溺人士的左右兩邊肺部液體是平均分佈，問李毓樺為何陳彥霖遺體的左右胸腔液差距如此大。李毓樺說未能解釋原因。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"orange\"><br />\n點解要俾警方交化驗所驗</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n會唔會俾人灌水入去個肺？ <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/noodles.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-01T05:43:42.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200901/NSF37OWTQFEBZPCGEXAYRTRB4E/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?